      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003ePrice Elasticity Analyzer\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n     This app helps you understand how changes in price affect product demand. It uses machine learning to estimate price elasticity and predict the impact of pricing decisions, enabling smarter pricing, promotion, and forecasting strategies.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \r\n    \r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThe app uses transaction records with the following fields:\r\n     \u003cp\u003eProduct (SKU) · Country / Region / Store · Category / Subcategory · Sector · Price Change (%) · Forecast Horizon (months)\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThe app generates:\r\n     \u003cp\u003ePrice parabola · Elasticity estimate · Forecasted sales after price change · Revenue impact · Sales trend chart\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Find the Right Price Point:  See exactly where to set prices to maximize sales revenue across different products and markets.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Make Better Sales Forecasts:  Account for how price changes will actually impact demand for specific products in specific regions.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Design Smarter Promotions: Determine optimal discount levels that drive volume without sacrificing margin.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Price New Products Confidently: Use data from similar products to set initial prices that will achieve target sales volumes.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Test Before You Implement: Run simulations to see the real financial impact of price changes before making decisions\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
